   SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "0"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "16e48a99-8075-456a-85ca-b3cb6bc4dc1e"],
 " is the initial angle of displacement, and the angular frequency of \
oscillation \[Omega] is given by"
