  3.9144170594791994`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1bde4a04-c887-4cf4-97ac-\
fee95e496685"],

Cell["\<\
Finally, we need to note that the momentum of this system is given by\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.914415669020136*^9, 
  3.9144156859250975`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"cc6651d4-9e41-4b19-b38e-\
c7d3cb28e010"],

